<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
      .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
      .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to ScheduleEase!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.name %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Thank you for joining ScheduleEase. We're excited to help you manage your appointments and schedules more efficiently.</p>
      
      <% unless @user.email_verified? %>
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> Please verify your email address to access all features of your account.</p>
      <% end %>
      
      <p>Here's what you can do with ScheduleEase:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><%= @user.provider? ? 'Set your availability and manage bookings' : 'Book appointments with your favorite providers' %></li>
        <li>Receive notifications for upcoming appointments</li>
        <li>Manage your schedule in one convenient place</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>
        <a href="<%= @frontend_url %>/dashboard" class="button">Get Started</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>The ScheduleEase Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© <%= Date.current.year %> ScheduleEase. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 